### 3.7 Validation Helpers — `Validate`

**Import:** `import Validate from '@/utils/Validate';`

Use for server-side validation checks beyond what DTOs cover (e.g., in service methods):

```typescript
if (!Validate.mongoId(userId)) throw new BadRequestException('Invalid user ID');
